recipes.title: Shakshuka With Feta
recipes.readyInMinutes: Här möts sparrisen lena smak och chilimajonnäsens hetta i en lättlagad och vacker vårrätt. Sparrisen grillas snabbt och toppa därefter med gochujangmajonnäsen, krispiga sjögräschips och koriander.
recipes.servings: 3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil, 1 large onion, halved and thinly, 3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil, 1 large onion, halved and thinly3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil, 1 large onion, halved and thinly3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil, 1 large onion, halved and thinly
recipes.instructions: Put in a greased and floured cake pan. Bake at 325-350 degrees for 1 1/2 hours. Save some cherries and nuts to decorate the top with. This makes a large cake and can be kept in the refrigerator for days.
